PostContactSummary.Content: The customer and agent discussed the possibility of implementing a call summarization feature. The agent explained that the current contact lens technology could potentially be used for this purpose, but they would need to evaluate the accuracy of the transcription first. The agent suggested exploring other options like using Hugging Face models if the accuracy is not satisfactory. The customer and agent agreed to further investigate the approaches to enhance the accuracy and make the solution production-ready, including integrating knowledge from the customer's website and FAQs. They decided to have a follow-up discussion with more details on the approach and the effort required.
